PETROLEUM CARRIER CORPORATION, a corporation, v. STANDARD OIL COMPANY OF KENTUCKY, a corporation. 23 So. (2nd) 249

June Term, 1945

September 11, 1945 Division A Martin Sack and R. C. Evans for Appellant. Thomas Sale for appellee. PER CURIAM:

No error appearing in the judgment appealed from, the same is affirmed.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BUFORD and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
